        "- `ArtBench-10/ArtBench-10.csv`\n",
        "\n",
        "If you do not have it on the folder, download from kaggle directly:\n",
        "\n",
        "https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/alexanderliao/artbench10\n"
      ]
